snippet.title: WEDNESDAY SEASON 2: PART 2 – TRAILER | September 3 | Netflix
snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— WEDNESDAY SEASON 2: PART 2

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Wednesday Season 2 Part 2, the story continues after Wednesday Addams’ brutal fall during her confrontation with Tyler’s unleashed Hyde form, leaving her on the edge of death and Nevermore Academy plunged into turmoil. Her decision to expose the LOIS program and free the imprisoned Outcasts at Willow Hill has unleashed threats far more dangerous than Judi and her Avian powers, shattering the fragile balance between Normies and Outcasts. With Tyler spiraling without a master, raven swarms gathering ominously, and whispers surrounding the fate of Morticia’s missing sister Ophelia, Wednesday faces a web of betrayal, bloodshed, and family secrets while her psychic powers remain dormant. As alliances crumble and enemies close in, she must confront the darkness she’s unleashed—perhaps even embracing the monster within—before the chaos consumes everything she’s sworn to protect.

—  Subscribe to Teaser Universe 🎬
—  For inquiries: teaseruniverse@gmail.com 📩

Lyrics:
I’ve been thinking 
That I got no idea what you’re thinking 
Are you happy? Are you sad?
Are you always gonna hate me for that night in Tokyo? 
When it ended 
I kinda hoped that it’d be open ended
But you never looked back 
Well I guess you can’t hold on to something once you let it go 
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I guess that I’m taking what I can get 
‘Cause I don’t get nothing new from your friends 
If you got the harder side of the break 
Then why is it harder for me to take 
There’s so much I might never get to say, ay
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I-I-I know it’s only in my mind
Playing three nights on the stereo
Like a movie scene, DiCaprio 
Oh l-I-I put my make up on just to fall asleep
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is something we’ll never be
It’s bittersweet
Can we be friends at least

snippet.title: İHTİYAÇ YOK OTELE - ERAY067 & MANSUR | CLTR LIVE S2 B3 |
snippet.description:
#ERAY067 ve #Mansur 'un #CLTRLIVE performansı #İhtiyaçYokOtele yayında. Canlı performans serimizin S2 B3 bölümü #CLTRhouse kanalında sizlerle!


Executive Producer: Akif Coşkuner
Sound Engineer : YAPARSOVUNUENES
Creative Director: Mert Dan
Post Production: Double Media

Her hafta yeni performanslar için abone olmayı ve bildirimleri açmayı unutma. CLTR LIVE videoları artık CLTR House kanalında!

CLTR House, #CultureRecords markasıdır. Tüm hakları saklıdır. 


SÖZLER : 

Tüm gece gözler açık,
Benz’in üstü açık,
İhtiyaç yok otele.

En yakın arkadaşım,
O benim sırdaşım,
Onu değişmem ele.

Endişelenme,
Beni düşünme,
Günün sonunda gelicem yanına.

Beni arama,
İki kadeh içince zaten sen geliyorsun yanıma.

Ben yazarken ağladım,
Sen dinlerken ağlama,
Dile kolay.

Üç senemi harcadım,
Kalan ömrümü de harcarım,
Sana feda.

Hep elveda...
Yüzümüz gülmedi aşktan yana,
Mutlu görünse de mutsuz resimler,
Yaralar oldu yanıma kalan.

Yaralar var ve yeni değil,
İstanbul, seni yeneceğim.
Anlatırdım da yeri değil,
Bi kadına mı yenileceğim?

Delale,
Götürdün aklımı başımdan, söyle.
Delale,

snippet.description:

► https://wraithesports.com/enskrzobs

Dakikalar:
00:00 Giriş
00:34 Oyunculuk Performansları ve Oyunun Açılışı
02:57 Açık Dünya ve Oyun Yapısı
04:04 Oynanış ve Aksiyon
08:15 Hikaye
09:26 Yarı spoilerlı kısım
11:13 Genel Değerlendirme ve Puanlama
11:36 YORUM OKUMACA!
17:11 Sponsor: OBSBOT (Wraith Esports)

Bu video içerisinde Mafia serisinin 4. oyunuyla ilgili sevdiğim sevmediğim şeyler üzerine konuşup, alınır mı alınmaz mı ona değiniyoruz. Ben tabii bir Mafia sevdalısı olarak çok objektif olduğumu söyleyemem. Ama yine de seriyle çok alakanız olmasa da hoşunuza gidecek ya da gitmeyecek şeylere değinmeye çalıştım.

Lyrics:

لانعي حالي 
عاللي جرالي 
تعصف فيي رياح الويل 
مخاوي نجوم الليل

تاهوا دروبي 
شمسي غروبي 
يصطف الحزن بالدور 
يطلع هالنفس بالزور
 
علاش تروح تخليني
بدال الدم الي فيني
يجري سم وينهيني
 شوي شوي 

علاش تروح وبلايا 
تنسى طريقي وهوايا
كيف تتبدل النوايا 
الدم يصير مي 

ياما سندتهن يا أنا وهي أنا وحدي بقيت
أخدوك لحم .. وعضم؛ للذيابة رميوك
ياما ضويتلهن درب وبالعتم وحدي عميت
لولا نفيساً جوهرك ياجنيد ماباعوك.

ياما ياصاحب حذرت مالن أمان 
ياجود بجافوك بليالي وضحاهم ياما راهنت عليهن وخسرت الرهان لكن اصالة  معدنك بيسان تسواهم

علاش تروح تخلينيبدال الدم الي فيني يجري سم وينهيني
 شوي شوي علاش تروح وبلايا تنسى طريقي وهواياكيف تتبدل النوايا الدم يصير مي 


رغم اني ابن اليوم 
زعلان عاللي راح 
محرومة عيني النوم
كلي جراح

كونو العين بالعين
وحياة ضو العين
رد الصاع صاعين
حتى ارتاح

علاش تروح تخلينيبدال الدم الي فيني يجري سم وينهيني
 شوي شوي علاش تروح وبلايا تنسى طريقي وهواياكيف تتبدل النوايا الدم يصير مي

snippet.title: CANAVAR PİTBULL MONSTER GERİ DÖNDÜ VE AİLEMİZİ KURTARDI! - GTA 5 PİTBULL'UN HAYATI
snippet.description:
